{"title":"时间转换","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":512,"url":"http://www.tsinsen.com/A1022","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div id=\"pcont1\" style=\"margin-top:20px; display:block;\">\n"},{"title":"问题描述","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pdcont\">　　给定一个以秒为单位的时间t，要求用“&lt;H&gt;:&lt;M&gt;:&lt;S&gt;”的格式来表示这个时间。&lt;H&gt;表示时间，&lt;M&gt;表示分钟，而&lt;S&gt;表示秒，它们都是整数且没有前导的“0”。例如，若t=0，则应输出是“0:0:0”；若t=3661，则输出“1:1:1”。</div>"},{"title":"输入格式","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pdcont\">　　输入只有一行，是一个整数t（0&lt;=t&lt;=86399）。</div>"},{"title":"输出格式","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pdcont\">　　输出只有一行，是以“&lt;H&gt;:&lt;M&gt;:&lt;S&gt;”的格式所表示的时间，不包括引号。</div>"},{"title":"样例输入","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pddata\">0</div>"},{"title":"样例输出","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pddata\">0:0:0</div>"},{"title":"样例输入","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pddata\">5436</div>"},{"title":"样例输出","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pddata\">1:30:36</div>\n\n</div>\n"}]}